DURABLE DISHWASHER RACK - Fit to withstand multiple cycles, this dishwasher basket is for the long term. Eliminate the need to replace it time and again. The grid design allows ventilation and drainage.

GREAT COMPATIBILITY - This dishwasher basket fits most leading brands and models in the market today. Please check your dishwasher specifications to ensure compatibility. It's the one universal dishwasher basket you need for several machines.

EASY ORGANIZATION - Our replacement basket rack comes with eight (8) ample-sized compartments. So now, keeping your utensils clean, and accessible. Kitchen organization becomes a convenient and fun undertaking.

APPLIANCE PROS YEAR WARRANTY - With no compromise to quality; we provide premium, certified products for a seal of ultimate safety. This dishwasher basket has been quality tested and is backed by the Appliance Pros 1-year limited warranty.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 1, 2023
reviews.reviewText: When I bought my house my dishwasher didn’t have a silverware basket in it and this one fits perfectly! I hate washing silverware by hand so I’m glad this is a great long lasting quality basket.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 21, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Fits my small kenmore dishwasher and you can separate it too!
reviews.reviewText: Fits my small apartment size kenmore dishwasher perfectly. I have way too many flatware to wash than dishes. The piece can separate in to two pieces which is even better to space out for flatware sterilization (needed nowadays) . I didn’t realize this at first but now I’m even happier with my purchase.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 7, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Didn’t fit perfectly, but cheap and just what I needed
reviews.reviewText: This was super cheap compared to the one made for my brand dishwasher. It didn’t fit perfectly (kind of had to shove it on),but for the money it was worth it. We really needed the extra room for utensils. Quality seems good.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 2, 2022
reviews.reviewText: The item can be split into two separate units!! This allows for placement in multiple different locations within a variety of dishwasher brands! Love it!!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 18, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice to Have for Silverware Cleaning
reviews.reviewText: I ordered this for a family member who has several people now living with her and uses a lot more silverware. My Mom said that she separated the basket into two parts and has the smaller one on the upper rack for tea spoons, with the other part on the lower rack. So far both baskets are working well in dishwasher with no issues.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 21, 2021
reviews.reviewText: Even though the basket is nice, it does not fit in my Kenmore dishwasher. It's too square and the handle is too tall. It doesn't fit in the front or sides of the bottom rack, and it does not allow the dishwasher prongs to go up through the basket, making the basket too tall. I will keep it to use with my picnic table. I might try to drill holes in the bottom.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 16, 2022
reviews.reviewText: I bought this to replace the utensil holder for my dish washer and this was so much better then the original factory piece. The piece was so easy to put together and the price was right. My husband was so happy that he does not have to fight with the utensil rack anymore. We are very satisfied customers.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on May 26, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Just what I needed, fits great in my Frigidaire dishwasher.
reviews.reviewText: My new dishwasher came with only one small silverware holder. So I ordered this one and it is perfect! This one will hold a lot of silverware and other small items, like plastic measuring cups, etc.It even matches the inside of my dishwasher, which is a Frigidaire. First pic is this one, second pic is the one that came with the dishwasher. Now if I have LOTS of dirty silverware, like on Thanksgiving, I can use both!
